headline: Smurfit Westrock (NYSE:SW): Assessing Valuation After Analyst Upgrades Signal Confidence Post-Merger
summary: Smurfit Westrock (NYSE:SW) grabbed the spotlight this week as several analysts issued upgrades, highlighting renewed optimism for the company’s direction after its recent merger. These moves come despite volatility in the broader paper and packaging sector. See our latest analysis for Smurfit Westrock.
